  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CFortitude\uFF1E (When this Digimon with digivolution
    cards is deleted, play this card without paying the cost).[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    Reveal the top card of your deck. If that card is a level 5 or lower Digimon
    card with \uFF1CFortitude\uFF1E, play it without paying the cost. Add the rest
    to your hand.[Your Turn] All of your Digimon with \uFF1CFortitude\uFF1E and no
    digivolution cards gain \uFF1CRush\uFF1E (This Digimon can attack the turn it
    comes into play)."
